Package org.epochx.ge.op.init

Interface Summary
GEInitialiser Initialisers are responsible for constructing the initial population that the XGE system will evolve.
 

Class Summary
FixedLengthInitialiser Initialisation implementation which constructs each program's chromosome to a specified length with a random sequence of codons.
FullInitialiser Initialisation implementation which constructs each program's chromosome while ensuring that it maps to a full parse tree of the specified depth.
GrowInitialiser Initialisation implementation which constructs each program's chromosome while ensuring that the parse tree it maps to is under the initial maximum depth limit.
RampedHalfAndHalfInitialiser Initialisation implementation which uses a combination of full and grow initialisers to create an initial population of GECandidatePrograms.
